{"tid":2160793,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國公司控華大基因侵權 求禁相關公司出售基因測序試劑套裝","createTime":"2020-08-17T07:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T11:20:14.000Z","uid":14918,"like":362,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"ef623972def37d1d1c726bb7294075a81038c756","tid":2160793,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:50:48.000Z","msg":"受港府欽點推行全民自願性病毒檢測的華大基因，上周五遭專門研發及生產基因組測序儀的英國公司入稟本港高等法院，指華大及其相關公司推出的基因測序試劑套裝侵犯其香港註冊的專利。原告要求法庭頒下禁制令，禁止華大供應和銷售該些侵權套裝、<span class=\"red\">銷毀所有存貨，以及向原告賠償。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200817/YOBYBBRSIBHEBDCZAD4QQYACCU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200817%2FYOBYBBRSIBHEBDCZAD4QQYACCU%2F&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=57ac7e2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200817%2FYOBYBBRSIBHEBDCZAD4QQYACCU%2F&h=440247fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200817/YOBYBBRSIBHEBDCZAD4QQYACCU/</a><br />\n<br />\n原告亦要求法庭頒下禁制令，禁止被告以及其轄下的任何公司及員工侵犯、授權他人侵犯該專利，或抄襲相類同的設計。原告要求法庭禁止被告製造涉及上述專利的多款高通量測序試劑套裝，不准被告擅自將其推出市場，並禁止被告銷售、進口、貯存、供應及推廣該些套裝。<br />\n<br />\n被告須在命令頒佈後7天內撤回任何侵權的宣傳產品，以及14天內將侵權產品交出並由原告銷毀。被告亦須向原告交代侵權產品的銷售對象、以及已獲利益等資料，並就原告的損失作出賠償。"},{"pid":"758dac9342ce1a372855f8895d65e10da6cf3ca9","tid":2160793,"uid":14918,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:51:38.000Z","msg":"【案件編號：HCIP47/20】"},{"pid":"b7ffafd3c3fe9adf879053cd8baad88b9320358e","tid":2160793,"uid":38317,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:52:39.000Z","msg":"G chi <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3708093651c965dfa8d2e42a43f0251d8ec04b4c","tid":2160793,"uid":14918,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:52: